    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A group of writing systems that are descended from the Brahmi script of ancient India, and now used throughout South Asia, Southeast Asia, East Asia, and formerly in Japan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
